{"tid":1096491,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你唔開心嘅話我會陪住你","createTime":"2019-04-07T17:46:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T03:33:58.000Z","uid":90595,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cfe1126d3f507d719525955fb05df75a3a558e96","tid":1096491,"uid":90595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T17:46:24.000Z","msg":"To me and to you,<br />\n<br />\n千其唔好怪自己﹐你好好﹐你已經做得好好。<br />\n冇一個人係完美﹐你要相信自己好嘅一面係多過差嘅一面﹐而呢個事實係一定會有人見到。<br />\n<br />\n唔知你知唔知﹐其實唔係你嘅錯﹐真係唔係。<br />\n每個人嘅長大環境係好影響一個人嘅性格﹐特別係屋企環境﹐佢地以前冇俾好嘅環境你﹐但將來你同人建立嘅環境一定會比以前自己經歷嘅好。短期你可能未必見到﹐但再過多幾年一定會好好多。<br />\n<br />\n我知你一定覺得好辛苦﹐因為生活係好辛苦。<br />\n如果你放棄自己﹐就再冇機會建立將來好好嘅嗰個家庭﹐咁樣會好可惜。<br />\n<br />\n我會喺到聽你講野﹐只要你想你隨時都可以搵我架﹐只要你願意講﹐你知我聽到嘅。"},{"pid":"2e92a7b015f8ad0c8fc073df8b44665b49808d3e","tid":1096491,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T18:42:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />炸彈到咗隻手落枱面"},{"pid":"3d2b6b9959d885980ce4b5cc996d09ba68292366","tid":1096491,"uid":90595,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2e92a7b015f8ad0c8fc073df8b44665b49808d3e","tid":1096491,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T18:42:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />炸彈到咗隻手落枱面"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T00: